# 🔟 Numerical Example

### Given

| Process | Arrival | Burst |
| ------- | ------: | ----: |
| P1      |       0 |     6 |
| P2      |       2 |     4 |
| P3      |       4 |     2 |

### FCFS Gantt Chart

```text
0------6----10----12
 P1      P2    P3
```

### Completion Times

| Process | CT |
| ------- | -: |
| P1      |  6 |
| P2      | 10 |
| P3      | 12 |

### Turnaround Time

| Process | TAT |
| ------- | --: |
| P1      |   6 |
| P2      |   8 |
| P3      |   8 |

### Waiting Time

| Process | WT |
| ------- | -: |
| P1      |  0 |
| P2      |  4 |
| P3      |  6 |

Average Waiting Time:

```text
(0 + 4 + 6)/3 = 3.33 ms
```

