# 1️⃣1️⃣ Common GATE Traps

### Trap 1

Waiting Time ≠ Turnaround Time.

---

### Trap 2

Round Robin requires the **Time Quantum**.

---

### Trap 3

SJF is optimal **only if burst times are known**.

---

### Trap 4

Priority Scheduling may cause **Starvation**.

---

### Trap 5

Aging prevents starvation.

